PLEASE TAKE TIME TO READ THIS!!!
(Except you can skip the random introduction crap if you want xD)

EDIT: I changed my YouTube name from corkplaysMC to MindlessGaming so I could be free to play other things than Minecraft, but the link is still corkplaysmc, but don't freak out :)

Random Introduction Crap:
Ok so once I left Avicus I deleted all videos on my channel and basically left gaming for half a year.
Now that I'm back, so is my youtube channel! This time though it is not solely focused on Minecraft, but don't worry mods, I will only let you guys know about Avicus related vids.
Once you have subscribed comment here and I will add you to the list. If you are already subscribed just let me know and I will add you as well.
My channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/corkplaysmc

The giveaway:
As old Avicus members know, I do some fun giveaways xD :)
So far, I believe I have spent about $200 on other players buying them ranks, sometimes for a giveaway, sometimes just because! I also buy OptiFine capes for people, but nothing else.
So far I have bought: MLGPorky a gold rank, RemyleOuistiti a gold rank, Ducksfanwaterloo an Emerald upgrade, Ironsoldier2000 a gold rank, Zedther an Optifine cape, 31778 a gold rank, and more people I have forgotten about xD

What will be the giveaway:
I will be doing anything at or under $50, this time there will only be 1 winner, sometimes there are multiple.
Popular giveaway choices: Gold rank, Emerald rank, Gold to Emerald upgrade, Emerald to Diamond upgrade, a Minecraft account, and an OptiFine cape.

How to get into the giveaway:
Just subscribe to my account (linked above and below) and then comment here in this format:

Username:
Youtube account name that subscribed:
Prize you want:

If you are already subscribed just let me know in your application

Once again, a link to my channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/corkplaysmc
Thanks guys! Remember to subscribe!!! :D
